data.description: Move in ready, lovingly maintained, three bedroom, two bath ranch on a spacious lot with fruit trees, garden space and plenty of room to enjoy the outdoors. Appliance package includes a brand new refrigerator and double convection oven with built-in air fryer. Thoughtful floor plan with spacious mudroom off of garage featuring a laundry room and pantry. Convenient to everything that North Georgia has to offer; especially the new hospital, grocery store and restaurants being built mere minutes away. Centrally located so you can enjoy the wineries and picturesque downtown in Dahlonega, the restaurants of Gainesville and the shopping in Dawsonville. You'll find comfort, convenience and affordability all in one clean, tidy, well built and cared for package.
